bio.employment: Founder of Your Car Buying Advocate
bio.openEndedText:
We are Mike & Corrie Rumple, owners of Your Car Buying Advocate, a car buying concierge service, created to find, locate and negotiate car deals for consumers who have said see-ya-never to the ever-so-common anxiety, stress and time wasting process of buying a car the traditional dealership way. 

We advocate for 🚙 buyers across all 50 states and we’re building a network of Advocates in 2022 to help more and more people. 🎉

💡Mike was a former car salesman until he turned consumer advocate in 2017.

You can read our story here:

www.youcarbuyingadvocate.com/confessions-of-a-former-car-salesman

About our fam…
👨🏼‍💼🙎🏼‍♀️🐵🙈🙉 We have three kids, gagillions of legos buried deep in our carpet and mysterious writings that appear on our walls from time to time. 🖍👦🏼(5) 👦🏼 (4) 👧🏼 (2) 🤔

We have a wild and crazy life but enjoy the excitement and challenges of being married and business partners (yikes!) while balancing raising kids. 🤪

My favorite car I have owned was the Lincoln MKZ. I loved how smooth the ride was. When I don’t need an SUV to tote around kids and friends and baseball gear and a million groceries, I think I’ll return to my first love. 💕 Until then, there’s Turo. -Corrie

We hope you enjoy our vehicle and we look forward to providing 
clean, convenient, safe and comfortable transportation.

Thanks For Renting With,
The Rumple’s

We are dedicated to providing our customers with an exceptional and memorable driving experience. Our mission is to offer a fleet of pristine, top-quality luxury and affordable vehicles, coupled with unmatched customer service. We aim to cater to the desires of discerning individuals who seek not just transportation,  but a statement of their refined taste and style.  We have vehicles that can meet every budget, and are able to accommodate parties of two or twelve individuals. Thank you for considering our vehicles you will not be disappointed.
